title: Jessica Simpson: Blonde. Billionaire. Boss | The Newlyweds Game | 2
description:
As things within the Simpson family deteriorate, Jessica puts her faith in the only stable person in her orbit: her boyfriend Nick Lachey. Together, they take the world by storm with their MTV reality show The Newlyweds. There’s just one problem — while the show is catapulting Jessica to newfound fame, it’s leaving Nick in the dust.
